Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...head for the New World,\Nthe second half of the Grand Line.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with Trafalgar Law and \Nhave come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped in the Birdcage \Nalong with the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On top of that, he put prices on \Nthe heads of Luffy and 11 others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now they're being hunted \Nby all the citizens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the Straw Hats fighting \Nthe Don Quixote Family fiercely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:04:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Law are heading \Nto the Royal Palace!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!\NLet's go and kick Mingo's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo isn't someone\Nthat you can beat just by force of will alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to cool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How can I cool down\Nafter getting this far?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, if you don't,\Nyou can't defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stopping here won't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law and Straw Hat have shown up\Nin the yard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...nearby the pool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Roger that.\N--Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent such a long time,\Nincreasing their number little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tens of thousands of toy slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...brought it all to naught in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet, Kanjuro?! We have no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just touch them with this hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll bring...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your existences...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to naught!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"One Shot One Kill!\NThe Man Who Will Save Dressrosa!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this is it! It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Usopp-{\i1}dono{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a work after my own heart.\N--Oh, it's done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.86,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good! Well done, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it kind of looks terrible again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Terrible but fine!\NI'll use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going, keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your ammunition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll call it "Bagworm"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the special attack we need\Nto take down Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on your Clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me every move Sugar makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really do it\Nwith only her Clairvoyance?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other options.\NSugar is already on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a sniper!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering someone is what I do best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot an enemy without being seen\Nto protect my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola. I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar's walking towards those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Captain Tank! Hack!\N--Yes, King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand! We'll protect Usopp-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people are getting really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's confused.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might come after me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.57,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.68,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,us hurting our people is\Nexactly what Doflamingo wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we need to do now is\Nbuy time for the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old king man, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar is getting closer to those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, she can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eye on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch them all and\Nhand them over to Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Coming!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, don't hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they're here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We have to stop them, too!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:56.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ROYAL PALACE - THE POOL GARDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:10:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kicking someone's ass" is your answer\Nto everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?!\NIt's easier that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Neither Trafalgar Law nor \NMonkey D. Luffy know me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's easy to approach them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar came out into the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a kid here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Mom! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In such a place? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you lost?\N--Don't pay attention to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here\Nso hide somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen! None of us will run!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop right there!\N--Father-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get near Usopp-{\i1}dono{\i0}\Nat any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Hold it, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay focused!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me the exact location of the yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See the windows on the upper \Npart of the Rampart Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see Straw Hat and Law\Nin the first window right of the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are iron bars on the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many bars are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One vertical bar and\Nthree horizontal bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The length from the ground \Nof the yard to the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the window is about 1.2 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's about Sugar's height.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How big is the bottom pane\Nof the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,50 wide by 40 high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the size of the ammo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Sugar now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still behind the post.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, we've got to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have these!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar is gonna get between \Nthe two any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The target is behind the wall...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I miss, we'll lose Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have these. They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is it okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!\NShe said I can have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar came into the center of the pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's approaching them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.51,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stop shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hit her no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seas without you,\NI don't ever wanna see that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who will save this country?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see it, Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have it all your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's... going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see the aurac{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...of their presences!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Grown-Up Great Black Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Long-Range Attack! Bagworm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wind is blowing from west to east...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wind force scale: 4.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A slight tailwind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.36,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first booster, Exploding Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Slight ascent, then, \Nrelease the rear section.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two seconds later,\Nignite the second booster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The outer-cover comes off\Nand the ammo goes horizontally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna go through the lower left side of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe window on the Rampart Tower!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It passes through the wall\Nand goes straight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Straight to the target!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It trails off a little but\Nthat special ammo is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...meant to retraumatize the enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,AAAAARGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy, you don't even have to notice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.61,0:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're all right,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}just go ahead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Usopp-{\i1}dono{\i0}, what are you \Ngoing to do with this drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you turn it into a real object?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An object?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! It's gonna be an ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! She passed out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why're they going down themselves?!\N--The toys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.50,0:21:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed, Usopp-{\i1}kun{\i0}...\NYou're such a brilliant sniper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!\NYou brought down Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really?! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm stunned!\N--Did he really do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are both okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sugar-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.29,0:22:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, Mingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've just made it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the top floor of the Palace\Nwhere the decisive battle will take place!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.32,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me just make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.99,0:22:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law finally come face-to-face with\Ntheir sworn enemy, Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.36,0:23:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Provoking the two cunningly and\Nleading them around by the nose,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo launches vicious attacks \Nagainst them manipulating Bellamy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.66,0:23:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when Luffy's anger hits its peak,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law strike a \Nblow with all their might!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.66,0:23:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N"Anger Erupts! Luffy and Law's Ultimate Stratagem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
